<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Thiengtho, Thiengtho, Thiengtho!
 Pathien Bangkim bawlthei!
 Zingkal matakin ka pahchak lau hungto ina,
 Thiengtho, Thiengtho, Thiengtho!
 Hehpih leh Thilbawlthei!
 Pathien-a Mi Thum, Pumkhat a um chuh!

[V2]
 2. Thiengtho, Thiengtho, Thiengtho!
 Mithiengte'n a hun pak;
 Lalchutphah ma a khun in sana lukhuk kawihtha'n;
 Cherub leh Seraph-te Na ma ah a khun ui,
 Umsa, umzing leh hungum ding Lalpa.

[V3]
 3. Thiengtho, Thiengtho, Thiengtho!
 Thimna'n hun lieh mahleh;
 Gilote mit in Na lopina mu kimah leu,
 Nang mai Thiengtho Na hi, Nang lo adang umlo,
 Hatna, hehpih leh thienthona akim.

[V4]
 4. Thiengtho, Thiengtho, Thiengtho!
 Pathien Bangkim bawlthei;
 Na siemte'n Na min lei van leh Tuipi-a pak ding,
 Thiengtho, Thiengtho, Thiengtho!
 Hehpih leh Thilbawlthei!
 Pathien-a Mi Thum, Pumkhat-a um chu!</lyrics>
<title>HOLY, HOLY, HOLY!</title>
<hymn_number>3</hymn_number>
</song>